    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>The decline in average I.Q. scores would be most upsetting if one did not recall the large number of individuals with above-average I.Q.'s who made incredibly stupid decisions over recent decades in banking, insurance and politics. WILLIAM R. HERMAN  Wilmington, N.C.</p>
      </block>
